Installation
===========

1. The content of the website goes under the 'www' directory of
whichever Web Server you are using. To access the home page you
currently need to access /cnerg/index.php/home

2. To get the database running, visit cnerg/application/config/config.php
and configure the database connection settings. Preferably use MYSQL

3. Other specific settings are mentioned in the above config file, take an
overview to fix stuff up.

4. The MYSQL dump is provided in cnerg.dump here with. Apply it using
mysqldump and call the database as 'cnerg' or uniformity.

5. The website uses CodeIgniter, for complete docs: http://codeigniter.com/user_guide/
